1. Introduction
Welcome to Logo Maker, Creator & Design Editor App developed by iappTechnologies LLP ("we", "us", "our"). This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which we collect, use, maintain, and disclose information collected from users ("you", "your") of our mobile application.
2. Information We Collect
We may collect and process the following types of personal data:
Personal Data Provided by You:
When you use our app, you may provide us with personal information such as your email address, first name, and last name for registration and authentication purposes.
Usage Data:
We may collect information about how you use our app, such as the features you interact with and the time spent on each section.
Device Information:
We may collect information about your mobile device, including the device model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, and crash data for infrastructure monitoring.
3. How We Use Your Information
We process your personal data for the following purposes:
To Provide and Maintain Our Services:
This includes creating logos, posters, invitation cards, YouTube thumbnails, banners, business cards, Instagram posts, and stories using editable templates and custom shapes.
To Improve Our Services:
We analyze usage patterns and preferences to enhance user experience and optimize our app's performance.
To Communicate with You:
We may send you service-related notifications and updates.
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We may share your personal data with third-party service providers who assist us in providing and maintaining our app, such as hosting providers, analytics services, and cloud storage services. These third parties are contractually obligated to use your personal data only as necessary to provide the services to us.
5. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. You may also have the right to restrict or object to certain processing activities and to receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format.
7. Third-Party Services
Our app uses the following third-party services which may collect personal data:
Advertising:
AdMob for personalized advertising based on unique device identifiers and usage data.
Analytics:
Google Analytics for Firebase to analyze app usage and performance.
Infrastructure Monitoring:
Crashlytics for monitoring app stability and crash reports.
Managing Contacts and Sending Messages:
Firebase Cloud Messaging for sending push notifications.
