9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the effective date above. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
By using Logo Maker, Creator & Design Editor App, you consent to the processing of your personal data as described in this Privacy Policy.
